The orb just obtained will allow you to use a kind of arts
called Lost Arts when set into an orbment.
Lost Arts are extremely powerful arts from the Dark Ages,
with the orbs representing new elements not reflective of
In addition to these nonstandard elements, each orb has
three standard elements. These indicate which elemental
slots on a character's ARCUS they can be set into.
Lost Arts can only be used when a character has max EP.
They can only be cast once per battle, and once used, they
will consume the caster's EP entirely.
